{"tid":1114142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搵女朋友或老婆絕對要搵基督教徒","createTime":"2019-04-18T09:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T03:28:24.000Z","uid":117718,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2edf3504e762538870e90a6c503d9e9d7ae3adc9","tid":1114142,"uid":117718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:59:53.000Z","msg":"可以瘋狂出軌無限原諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n耶穌說：「我對你說，不是到七次，乃是到七十個七次。［馬太福音18:22］<br />\n<br />\n馬可福音 11:25,26<br />\n你們站著禱告的時候，若想起有人得罪你們，就當饒恕他，好叫你們在天上的父也饒恕你們的過犯。<br />\n<br />\n歌羅西書 3:13<br />\n倘若這人與那人有嫌隙，總要彼此包容，彼此饒恕；主怎樣饒恕了你們，你們也要怎樣饒恕人。<br />\n<br />\n以弗所書 5:1<br />\n所以你們該效法神，好像蒙慈愛的兒女一樣。"},{"pid":"c73b1a84f8ea6134429736adf39106fe532e4568","tid":1114142,"uid":191352,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T10:03:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20b0452b23900a344e17d97a2e0b63a6d1fc1fc8","tid":1114142,"uid":117718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c73b1a84f8ea6134429736adf39106fe532e4568","tid":1114142,"uid":191352,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T10:03:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T10:09:40.000Z","msg":"咁撚惡嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry囉<br />\n神說要寬恕別人啊"},{"pid":"56f3749bc8c33b55a4dab7ae1e275cb352bb7b09","tid":1114142,"uid":191352,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T10:10:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5af5c4f2afd2dc59182c902c05566f5e3101a23","tid":1114142,"uid":117718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56f3749bc8c33b55a4dab7ae1e275cb352bb7b09","tid":1114142,"uid":191352,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"20b0452b23900a344e17d97a2e0b63a6d1fc1fc8","tid":1